    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Anno ab incarnacione Domini millesimo centesimo
                        quintodecimo, temporibus <persName key="#Popes" ref="#people/52"
                            >Pascasii</persName> pape et <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/127">Henrici</persName> imperatoris, die duodecimo mensis
                        iunii, indictione octava, in loco qui dicitur <placeName ref="#places/3559"
                            >Lacus Sanctus</placeName>, in <rs key="#Houses">mansione</rs> iuxta <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3600">Sancti
                            Venancii</orgName>. In presencia <persName key="#Judge"><name
                                ref="Sassus">Saxonis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/2"
                            >Florencia</placeName> et Tigrimi de Vuidone, Deusdedit et Zazonis et
                        Ubaldi germanorum filiorum Seniorellus de Ubaldo et Petri de Rustico a Porta
                        Aurea et aliorum multorum, domnus <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/4307"
                            >Teucio</persName> venerabilis <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie in
                                <placeName ref="#places/4179">Ponposia</placeName></orgName> et
                        domnus <persName key="#Priors"><name ref="Rodualdus"
                            >Rodaldus</name></persName> prior et domnus <persName key="#Monks"><name
                                ref="Gregorius">Gregorius</name></persName> sitque domnus <persName
                            key="#Monks"><name ref="Hubertus">Ubertus</name></persName> et domnus
                            <persName key="#Monks"><name ref="Paulus">Paulus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monachi</rs> eiusdem monasterii representati fuerunt,
                        ostendentes illorum instrumenta presente <persName><name
                                ref="Oddo de Amabile">Oddone de Amabile</name></persName> cum filio
                        suo <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohanne</name></persName> et nepotibus
                        suis silicet <persName><name ref="Amabilis">Amabile</name></persName> filio
                                <persName><name ref="Deusdedit">Deusdedit</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Hieremias">Geremia</name></persName> filio
                                <persName><name ref="Andreas de Oddone">Andree de
                            Oddone</name></persName> et filio <persName><name ref="Oddolinus"
                                >Odolini</name></persName> fratris sui et duobus filiis
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes de Oddone">Iohanne de
                            Oddone</name></persName>, totis consanguineis litigantibus secum,
                        dicentibus se racionem abere de toto loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Placitum/iudicatum" ref="#places/3573">Vincarita</placeName>. Tunc
                        predictus abbas cum prefato priore et monachis parati fuerunt facere
                        securare per sacramentum hominibus ipsius loci Lacus Sancti antiquioribus
                        quod usque ad callem predicte Vincarite et usque ad <placeName
                            ref="#places/3574">Arzele quod vocatur Malum</placeName> sic est de
                        pertinencia iamdicti loci qui vocatur <geogName key="#Massae"
                            ref="#estates/2454">Lacus Sanctus</geogName> et infra <rs key="#Massae"
                            >massam</rs> eiusdem loci, secundum quod legitur in illo <rs
                            key="#Papal_concession">precepto</rs> ibidem relecto, quod fecerat
                        domnus <persName key="#Papal_concession #Popes" ref="#people/2137"
                            >Benedictus</persName> papa sancte Romane Ecclesie domno <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1574">Vuidoni</persName> sancto abbati
                        prefati monasterii et in alio precepto quod fecit domnus <persName
                            key="#Papal_concession #Popes" ref="#people/2140">Leo</persName> papa
                        predicte Romane Ecclesie domno <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1596"
                            >Mainardo</persName> abbati eiusdem monasterii, qui suprascripta <rs
                            key="#Confinia">latera</rs> in eodem precepto scribere iussit et in illo
                            <rs key="#Breve/memoratorium">breve</rs> investicionis factum ab
                            <persName key="#Breve/memoratorium #Popes" ref="#people/2144"
                            >Alexandro</persName> apostolico iamdicte Romane Ecclesie, qui
                        supradicta precepta per eundem brevem confirmavit, et latera in eis scripta
                        in eodem breve memoravit, eciam suis manibus designavit prefato Mainardo
                        abbati ut predictis Oddonibus minime pertinere videbatur neque suis
                        parentibus neque per illam cartam quam se ostendebant abere a <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3659">Sancta Maria in Aurigario</orgName> neque
                        per ullum modum vel racionem et per sexaginta annos et amplius illorum
                        monasterium abuit et detinuit, ita ut prenominati Oddones vel parentes
                        illorum nec abuerunt nec detinuerunt. Hec omnia parati fuerunt adimplere per
                        illos homines antiquiores ipsius loci Lacus Sancti qui supradictam rem
                        laboraverunt et fructus quos ibi Dominus dederat exinde perceperunt, iure
                        prescripti monasterii Sancte Marie in Pomposia. Hoc factum est sub die
                        menseque et indictione supradicta, in supradicto loco. Ego <persName
                            key="#Tabellio">
                            <name ref="Petrus de Dindone">Petrus de Dindo</name></persName>
                        <placeName ref="#places/594">Ravennas</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellio</rs> quia presens fui et audivi et vidi scripsi
                        hec omnia sicut superius leguntur.</ab>
                </div>
